{
  "stem": "26672.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She went and to her-- to her house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was introduced to the guy, a doctor, who lived in her house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, this is a woman, who's claiming her properties.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the guard from the town-hall left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this guy, who occupied the house, said, if you don't go out now, they'll carry you out at night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you better be aware.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said, that night, other people, Jews, who were still left from the camps, survived, there was a pogrom, quite a few were killed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She managed to hide yourself in a haystack and escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt, eventually, was in Lodz, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lodz, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- I was only there a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see there was-- I mean, the movements of the people then, there was always running to-- what we call it-- like the town-halls or the Jewish judenrat, to try and find names or whatever or getting vouchers for food.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody had anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was only controlled by the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, in turn, I suppose, by then, were getting it either from England and from-- from-- from America, from the [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Joint. ?] And that's how you, you-- the contact you had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wherever you went, there was thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Thousands?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were hundreds of people for the same reason, either getting vouchers for food or getting food or getting some sort of start now.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's all it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, from Lodz, you went back to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we-- we were told that we were going to go on to Palestine, the youth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had nothing left in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't want to be a-- a baby anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt wanted to bring me up as a-- as her child.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
